            {
                "title": "Probation Period",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "data": "Employees hired using Deel have a probation period of 30 days, which you can extend up to 180 days for managerial positions and specialized technical roles. As of January 2022, it's Deel company policy to include probation periods in all employment contracts moving forward."
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "data": "Probation periods help an employer and the employee ensure they're a hiring match, allowing a company to quickly decide if it's a fit or the employee to see if the job aligns with their career goals."
                    }
                ]
